org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects INNER JOIN wikis ON wikis.project_id = projects.id WHERE projects.status = 1 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'wiki') IS NOT NULL AND projects.id IN (1, 5)
